latestIgtvVideos.title: #Heartwork
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#Repost @bpraak
• • • • • •
When I came across the musical tribute of LAY'S #Heartwork, I could not help but share my rendition to this melody. This ode is dedicated to all those farmers, retailers, truck drivers and many other heroes who work relentlessly to bring joy to millions. A huge thank you to them for their efforts. And I truly appreciate this initiative by @Lays_India and @smilefoundationindia to provide hygiene kits to these communities. If you want to be a part of this cause then head to theheartwork.support and show some support to these heartworkers.

latestIgtvVideos.title: #Heartwork
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#Repost @nehakakkar
• • • • • •
In these tough times, our farmers, truck drivers and retailers have continued to keep a smile on our faces aur Ye.. Yeh Heartwork kehlata hai! ♥️👏🏼 .
Really appreciate the heart warming efforts of @Lays_India and @smilefoundationindia to support these rockstars by providing them with hygiene kits. If you wish to be a part of this beautiful initiative then share this film with your family and friends and log on to theheartwork.support.
#Heartwork #WeSupportYou #YehHeartWorkKehlataHai #NehaKakkar

latestIgtvVideos.title: #Heartwork
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#Repost @dhvanibhanushali22
• • • • • •
I saw this melodious tribute 'Ye Heartwork Kehlata hai', that appreciates the efforts of unsung heroes like farmers, truck drivers, retailers and many more who are working round the clock in these challenging times to bring joy to millions of people across the country. Would like to congratulate @lays_india for creating such a delightful ode and @smilefoundationindia for helping these heroes by providing them with hygiene kits. I have tried to thank these heroes by singing the ode. Hope you all like it. Do also check my story for more on this. Also, do share this with your friends and family and support the initiative by going to theheartwork.support.

latestIgtvVideos.title: #Heartwork
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#Repost @qaranx
• • • • • •
Despite all odds, our farmers, truck drivers, retailers and so many others like them have managed to keep us smiling during these difficult times. I would like to applaud @lays_india for creating such a delightful tribute in the form of “Yeh Heartwork Kehlata Hai” and partnering with @smilefoundationindia for helping these heroes by supporting them with Hygiene Kits. I support these heartworkers and you can too. Check out my story and support them by logging on to theheartwork.support. Spread the word. #Heartwork
